			<DIV>
<P>This is the list collected from the suggestion thread.&nbsp; On Monday I am going to start a thread asking you to vote for which port you would like added.&nbsp; You will be allowed to choose 3 from the list.&nbsp; From there we will discuss which ones to put on the list.&nbsp; Thank you all for your suggestions.&nbsp; Please use from now until Monday to add to this list.&nbsp; Thanks much!!!!!!</P>
<P><STRONG>Antonica<BR></STRONG>Everfrost – Under water caves<BR>Temple of Solusek Ro<BR>The Rathe Mountains<BR>Lake Rathe<BR>High Keep<BR>Qeynos Hills<BR>South Karana – There are already spires<BR>Oasis<BR></P>
<P><STRONG>Odus</STRONG><BR>Crypt of Nadox<BR>Dulak</P>
<P><STRONG>Faydwer</STRONG><BR>Steamfont<BR>Dagnor’s Cauldron<BR>Unrest<BR>Kedge Keep<BR>Lesser Faydark – Near Mistmoore</P>
<P><STRONG>Kunark</STRONG><BR>Lake of Ill Omen – Platform in the lake<BR>Frontier Mountains<BR>Chardok – Near Chardock B</P>
<P><BR><STRONG>Velious<BR></STRONG>Western Wastes<BR>Eastern Wastes<BR>Dragon Necropolis</P>
<P><STRONG>The Planes</STRONG><BR>Plane of Traquility<BR>Plane of Fear</P>
<P><STRONG>Kuua</STRONG><BR>Dranik’s Scar<BR>Riftseekers<BR>Ruined City of Dranik</P>
<P><STRONG>Ocean Zones</STRONG><BR>Ocean of Tears<BR>Timorous Deep<BR>Erud’s Crossing</P>
